Class Blocker

  • java.lang.Object
    • arena.Occupant
      • arena.Blocker

  • public class Blocker
extends Occupant
    A Blocker is a simple Occupant whose purpose is to block movement and shots. Blockers appear as gray blocks and do not belong to either team.
